before I give you the solution I wanna point to your mistakes maybe you wanna try to solve it on your own.
first mistake, you are starting with cleaning the whole string, which removes all (//s,.) so how would you know where was the last (.,)
second mistake, you should replace last ,. with . not first (think about it)

and the solution would be something like this 

        int lastIndex = Math.max(input.lastIndexOf(&#39;,&#39;), input.lastIndexOf(&#39;.&#39;));
        String cleanedInput = input.substring(0, lastIndex).replaceAll(&quot;[,\\s.]&quot;,&quot;&quot;)
                .concat(&quot;.&quot;+input.substring(lastIndex+1).replaceAll(&quot; &quot;,&quot;&quot;));
